OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBelfast: Fifteen           
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdrug-related deaths since  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FJune                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Fifteen people have died in Belfast as 
OL,6, a result of drugs overdoses since the  
OL,7, start of June, figures show.           
OL,9,FThe news was revealed during an        
OL,10,Femergency meeting of Belfast City      
OL,11,FCouncil on Friday to address the issue.
OL,13,FIt is understood there have been a     
OL,14,Ftotal of 34 such deaths in the greater 
OL,15,FBelfast area since the start of 2022.  
OL,17,FSDLP councillor Paul McCusker, who     
OL,18,Fcalled the meeting, said Belfast was "a
OL,19,Fcity in crisis".                       
